display_name: "SimpleOS Glass"
pulled_from: "projects/14134637940805933672 designTheme"
pulled_at: "2026-04-12"
notes: |
    Project 2 live designTheme. Uses TONAL_SPOT colorVariant (not explicit
    MD3 namedColors map). Typography/role mapping differs from Obsidian:
    body=INTER, headline=MANROPE, label=SPACE_GROTESK.

    Live designMd is the *shorter original* (~60 lines). The skill file
    .claude/skills/stitch.md has an expanded 140-line version that has
    not been pushed to Stitch. To sync them, push the skill's version
    via mcp__stitch__update_design_system when ready.

theme:
    color_mode: DARK
    color_variant: TONAL_SPOT
    custom_color: "#0A84FF"
    roundness: ROUND_TWELVE
    headline_font: MANROPE
    body_font: INTER
    label_font: SPACE_GROTESK
    override_primary_color: "#0A84FF"
    override_secondary_color: "#BB86FC"
    override_tertiary_color: "#30D158"
    override_neutral_color: "#1E1E23"
    named_colors: {}  # implicit from TONAL_SPOT

design_md: |
    # SimpleOS Glassmorphism Design Language

    ## Core Principle
    Every surface is a frosted glass pane floating over a deep-space gradient
    background. No flat solid backgrounds. All surfaces use semi-transparent
    backgrounds with backdrop-filter blur.

    ## Background
    - Dark gradient from #060612 (top) to #1A0830 (bottom) -- deep space feel
    - Light gradient from #C8B8E8 (top lavender) to #F0ECF5 (bottom soft white)

    ## Glass Surfaces (Dark Mode)
    - Primary: rgba(30,30,35,0.72) with backdrop-filter: blur(20px)
    - Secondary: rgba(40,40,48,0.52) with backdrop-filter: blur(20px)
    - Tertiary: rgba(50,50,58,0.36) with backdrop-filter: blur(8px)
    - Elevated (modals, popovers): rgba(44,44,50,0.88) with backdrop-filter: blur(40px)

    ## Borders
    - Subtle: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08)
    - Prominent: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.18)
    - Top edge highlight: 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.30) on top border

    ## Shadows (multi-layer depth)
    - Active windows: 9+ shadow layers creating realistic depth
    - Inactive windows: 3 layers, reduced alpha

    ## Window Chrome
    - Title bar: 24px, glass surface with blur, traffic light buttons
      (close #FF5F57, minimize #FFBD2E, maximize #28CA41) on left
    - Title text centered, 13px, secondary text color
    - 12px corner radius on window frame

    ## System Bar (top, 28px)
    - Full-width glass surface, blur(24px), nav-grade
    - Left: Logo + active app name + menu items
    - Right: Search, Control Center, Wi-Fi, battery %, volume, clock

    ## Dock (bottom)
    - Pill-shaped glass container, 58px tall, 26px corner radius
    - Icons: 40px with 48px pill background, 16px gap
    - Magnification on hover (scale 1.0 to 1.5)
    - Active indicator: 4px dot below icon

    ## Typography
    - Headline: Manrope 600-700, Body: Inter 400, Label: Space Grotesk 500
    - Text primary: #F5F5F7 (dark) / #1D1D1F (light)

    ## Colors
    - Accent: #0A84FF (iOS blue)
    - Secondary accent: #BB86FC (purple)
    - Semantic: error #FF453A, warning #FF9F0A, success #30D158, info #64D2FF

    ## DO NOT
    - Use flat solid colored backgrounds
    - Use sharp corners (minimum 8px radius)
    - Use heavy drop shadows without blur
    - Use bright white or pure black surfaces
    - Forget the gradient background behind all glass layers
